response.overview: A sailor prone to violent outbursts is sent to a naval psychiatrist for help. Refusing at first to open up, the young man eventually breaks down and reveals a horrific childhood. Through the guidance of his doctor, he confronts his painful past and begins a quest to find the family he never knew.
response.tagline: Antwone Fisher is at war... with himself.
response.title: Antwone Fisher

titles.title: El triunfo del espíritu: Antwone Fisher
